&lt;h1 id="venture-hacks-meetup-and-panel-at-sxsw"&gt;Venture Hacks Meetup and Panel at SXSW&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 10 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For those of you going to SXSW, I&amp;rsquo;ll be on the [Seed Combinators Panel](Seed Combinators Panel) on Monday March 15 3:30pm. I&amp;rsquo;m joining [Paul Graham](Paul Graham), [David Cohen](David Cohen), [Marc Nathan](Marc Nathan), and [Joshua Baer](Joshua Baer) to talk about YStars, TechCombinators, SeedBoxes, and the like. Here&amp;rsquo;s the &lt;a href="Plancast"&gt;Plancast&lt;/a&gt; if you want me to &amp;ldquo;count you in.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Attend talks and conferences, even those not directly related to your work</title><link>https://linguista.cn/terencetao/career-advice/orig/attend-talks-and-conferences-even-those-not-directly-related-to-your-work/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 19:01:36 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/terencetao/career-advice/orig/attend-talks-and-conferences-even-those-not-directly-related-to-your-work/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/terencetao/career-advice/zh/attend-talks-and-conferences-even-those-not-directly-related-to-your-work.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;
